  "actions": {
    "blocks": [
      {
        "name": "Crush",
        "text": "*Melee Weapon Attack:* atk[str] to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. *Hit:* dmg[1d6 + str] bludgeoning damage, and [name] attaches to the target. If the target is Medium or smaller and [name] has advantage on the attack roll, it attaches by engulfing the target's head, and the target is also blinded and unable to breathe while [name] is attached in this way.\n  While attached to the target, [name] can attack no other creature except the target but has advantage on its attack rolls. [name]'s speed also becomes 0, it can't benefit from any bonus to its speed, and it moves with the target.\n  A creature can detach [name] by making a successful DC 13 Strength check as an action. On its turn, [name] can detach itself from the target by using 5 feet of movement."
      },
      {
        "name": "Darkness Aura (1/day)",
        "text": "A 15-foot radius of magical darkness extends out from [name], moves with it, and spreads around corners. The darkness lasts as long as [name] maintains concentration, up to 10 minutes (as if concentrating on a spell). Darkvision can't penetrate this darkness, and no natural light can illuminate it. If any of the darkness overlaps with an area of light created by a spell of 2nd level or lower, the spell creating the light is dispelled."
      }
    ]
  },
